{"tid":16180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港府為遷就內地食品 剔除三種農藥規管","createTime":"2016-12-01T10:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T11:12:15.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb1006fedaece55733eebb2a996dbfb71dff87e4","tid":16180,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:32:59.000Z","msg":"政府制定《食物內除害劑殘餘規例》，規管300多種農藥於食物的殘留量，法例將於本年8月生效。但政府於本年1月向立法會提交修訂，建議將3種農藥剔出規管名單，3種農藥分別為三乙膦酸鋁、噻苯隆及三苯基氫氧化鍚，政府稱修訂來自一位「持份者」意見，但沒有說明詳細原因。有線電視新聞報道揭露，該「持份者」為內地國家質檢總局，港府將3種農藥剔出規管名單，是要為內地食品進入香港市場大開方便之門。<br />\n<br />\n有線電視新聞報道指，食物及衞生局初時拒絕直接講出「持份者」身份，推說「持份者」來自內地、日本、美國和加拿大等地官方機構，但有線電視新聞後來取得美國和加拿大駐港領事館回覆，否認曾向港府就規管農藥提供意見，食衞局才承認持份者為內地國家質檢總局。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述食衞局指，港府一向跟隨美國農藥規管標準，但後來發現若繼續採用此標準，部分內地進口香港的食物將超出規管中所含農藥標準而無法輸港，故將此3種農藥剔出規管名單。食衞局補充，該3種農藥毒性不高，即使從規管名單中除去亦不會提高市民的食物安全風險。<br />\n<br />\n對於食衞局的「有毒農藥無害論」，中文大學生命科學院副教授陳竟明指，該3種農藥中有一種明顯為高毒性農藥，而另外兩種農藥則屬中度毒性。"},{"pid":"359dd924a4342dac67504a80cf7f9844bd96e9ea","tid":16180,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:40:10.000Z","msg":"Chi 9 sin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全世界食物安全規定係越黎越嚴，只有支那行相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2d643c2b7f4f38b002139332dab35480d709ff","tid":16180,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:43:23.000Z","msg":"有毒XX無害 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b82f8cf2fa4d2f69090bec10926dc2f4497771c","tid":16180,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:44:42.000Z","msg":"又想搵鳩加拿大，政府哩班死產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7d3193ca53ce40276bd4c7217395a2438dcfbf","tid":16180,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8ea238e5f31ba7ded68e1c0afa26e57e4b905a","tid":16180,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:45:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又想搵鳩加拿大笨，政府哩班死產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"44609aeb00b31d1ed28e217f28261fd65b2e1094","tid":16180,"uid":4297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:48:15.000Z","msg":"嘩特衰去死啦<br />\n推到加返入去限制名冊"},{"pid":"1d2e1cc550525f13003e1574f9692c2aafdb562e","tid":16180,"uid":18634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 班官員有冇腦㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ac631f00116c24926c7412182b2f33ee8a5775","tid":16180,"uid":18555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老母特衰政府<br />\n無大毒性都係有， 邊會放寬， 只會收緊<br />\n都係去誠哥間taste買外國菜算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f698c5307dfedcde05c0f158cf1811abec3c28c6","tid":16180,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:53:41.000Z","msg":"好似好耐啦喎"},{"pid":"ab92f1093439f14057eaa2912d4a71a316ba82e6","tid":16180,"uid":9749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5858c92d5f0bc1b3d760defdf1f03556715f247d","tid":16180,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01